{
  "text": "Isolation of pNK cells. pNK cells were isolated from peripheral blood as previously described [CITATION_1] . For cytotoxicity assay, pNK were further purified by the subsequent use of anti-CD56-coated magnetic beads.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "1426132"
